'''''Love <U+2605> Gun''''' is a [[CD single]] by [[Japanese people|Japanese]] singer and [[Seiy<U+016B>|voice actress]] [[Aya Hirano]]. It was released on [[October 10]] [[2007]] and was produced by [[Lantis (company)|Lantis]].<ref>{{citeweb|url=http://us.yesasia.com/en/PrdDept.aspx/code-j/section-music/pid-1004961811/|title=Love <U+2605> Gun at Yesasia.com|accessdate=2007-10-13|language=Japanese}}</ref> This is Aya Hirano's fourth [[maxi single]] and her first release from her three-month consecutive single release campaign.<ref>{{citeweb|url=http://www.cdjapan.co.jp/detailview.html?KEY=LACM-4417|title=Love <U+2605> Gun at cdjapan.co.jp|accessdate=2007-11-26|language=Japanese}}</ref>

